snippet.title: Knåddskogen Trailer
snippet.description:
Available for free on itch: https://knoddskogen.itch.io/knddskogen

Knåddskogen is a single-player, exploration game where you take on the role as a kindergarten teacher searching for her missing class in the depths of the Swedish forest. It's a bizarre adventure, which turns an otherwise tough situation to something fun and quirky with a lot of humor.

Knåddskogen was made by 9 students during a 7 week course at Futuregames, a vocational school located in Stockholm, Sweden.
